Package de.romankreisel.LogViewer

Class Summary
LogfileParser Helper-Class to generate a list of LogRecords from a XML-File generated by java.util.logging.
LogTableModel TableModel for LogRecords.
LogViewer Class to make the LogViewer-Project runable as standalone-product.
LogviewFrame LogViewer-JFrame - use this class if you're searching for an easy way to embed LogViewer in your project.
LogviewPanel Use this class if you want to embedd the LogViewer in your own Frame.
MemoryHandler Handler for java.util.logging which collects the LogRecords in memory.
XMLLogfileInputStream Use this input-filter to parse XML-Files generated by java.util.logging it clears the input from invalid characters and closes the log of unfinished logfiles if necessary.
